{"tid":513193,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"雙重國籍過境莫斯科","createTime":"2017-12-29T09:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T04:26:32.000Z","uid":114088,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87b53d64a67763481a70e2b81bdcc643ce3b7751","tid":513193,"uid":114088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"嚟緊我去歐洲(non-申根國)用BNO出入境(免簽), 回程轉機停莫斯科, 有十幾個鐘會出市區玩, 咁果陣用本特區出入境有冇問題?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為去歐洲果陣用特區又要簽證(check左), 而俄羅斯嘅話用BNO要簽證但特區又唔洗.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係我個Trip會帶住兩本passport, 有冇咩風險? <br />\n<br />\n如果我冇理解錯:<br />\n<br />\n1. HKG &gt; EU, 上機check-in &amp; EU入境 - 用BNO<br />\n<br />\n2. EU -&gt; 莫斯科,  check-in用特區 (主要俾airline知特區可以免簽入俄羅斯), 出境BNO (海關蓋印)<br />\n<br />\n3. 莫斯科入境/出境 - 用特區<br />\n<br />\n4. 返到香港<br />\n<br />\n求達人指教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ab2922fefb789d8a2f7cbe4178bdc093875281","tid":513193,"uid":71425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"a97f4e1333d6deffdfabdd71685256fe6dc04ac9","tid":513193,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"用BNO搞俄國VISA啦，萬一在俄國有意外你首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae7ca712a57b6b9df1e36145f22af7b83a34676","tid":513193,"uid":33213,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a97f4e1333d6deffdfabdd71685256fe6dc04ac9","tid":513193,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"用BNO搞俄國VISA啦，萬一在俄國有意外你首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T22:30:46.000Z","msg":"喺俄佬地頭揸乜都當你支那人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n看得自己那麼高.jpg"},{"pid":"a8f588450602cca45528320ab09c9e0a9a0f82df","tid":513193,"ui